						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/one-mans-trash-reflections-on-a-failed-novel/" title="One Man’s Trash: Reflections on a Failed Novel">One Man’s Trash: Reflections on a Failed Novel</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
											<div class="cell auto tertiary-story">
					<div class="story-img-container">
						<a href="https://lithub.com/on-the-haunted-history-of-apartheid-in-south-africa/" title="On the Haunted History of Apartheid in South Africa"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/The-Writer-by-Ruth-Chaney-1943-2-1-300x300.jpg"></a>
					</div>
					<div class="story-content-container">
						<h2><a href="https://lithub.com/on-the-haunted-history-of-apartheid-in-south-africa/" title="On the Haunted History of Apartheid in South Africa">On the Haunted History of Apartheid in South Africa</a></h2>
